This paper deals with cyber attacks on in-vehicle networks and proposes a new attack called the cloaking attack. The paper discusses the implementation and testing of the attack on intrusion detection systems (IDSs) and proposes a new metric to quantify the effectiveness of the attack. Based on this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
